33:58.513 --> 33:59.674
I'm not aware of it.

34:00.015 --> 34:04.381
When I'm starting, I think of... I'm a one-language person, unfortunately.

34:04.401 --> 34:05.402
No, I think it just sort of...

34:06.243 --> 34:09.447
